description.narrative:
The Strategic Sector Cooperation on Statistics aims to improve the statistical system of Ghana and therewith the foundation for evidence-based policy making and democracy – through increased availability of internationally comparable, independent, accurate and timely statistics by:

-Increasing the use of administrative data sources for statistical production; 
-Improving IT with focus on data storage and dissemination; 
-Improving quality and methodology in statistical production, which is harmonized throughout the institution; 
-Improving accuracy and coverage of economic statistics; 
-Training staff in general statistical competences.
